Stage 1
Collect investment amount
Collect annual interest rate in percentage
Enter the number of years
Calculate the accumulated value 
Display the accumulated value

Stage 2
1. Prompt user to enter investment amount 
2. Collect the investment amount from the user
3. store the investment amount collected from the user as investmentAmount
4. Prompt user to enter annual interest rate 
5. Collect the interest rate from the user
6. store the interest rate collected from the user as interestRate
7. Prompt user to enter number of years 
8. Collect the number of years from the user
9. Calculate monthly interest rate
10. Store the value monthlyInterestRate
11. store the number of years collected from the user as numberOfYears

Calculate 

investmentAmount * Math.power((1 + interestRate), numberOfYears

Store as returnOnInvestment
Print result